OL,5, Russell T Davies says he wants to write
OL,6, a darker LGBTQ+ drama as he feels there
OL,7, is "a lot of hatred in the air".       
OL,9,FSpeaking at the Iris Prize, the largest
OL,10,FLGBTQ+ short film prize in the world,  
OL,11,Fthe It's a Sin writer and producer said
OL,12,Fhe was worried about "where we are     
OL,13,Fnow".                                  
OL,15,FDavies, whose work also includes Queer 
OL,16,Fas Folk, said his writing always came  
OL,17,Fback to the "here and now".            
OL,19,F"I have things to say about that," he  
OL,20,Fadded.                                 
